      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Sept 19 review of play A Lesson Before Dying, which misstate surname of director, Kent Thompson</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A theater review yesterday about ''A Lesson Before Dying,'' by Romulus Linney, at the Signature Theater Company, misstated the surname of the play's director. As noted in the credits, he is Kent Thompson, not Anderson.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A theater review yesterday about ''A Lesson Before Dying,'' by Romulus Linney, at the Signature Theater Company, misstated the surname of the play's director. As noted in the credits, he is Kent Thompson, not Anderson.</p>
      </block>
